Developer Terms of Use
des: Tell us your birthday and we generate a prophecy for you based on your birthday and the current star constellation. We are a group of fortune-tellers, astrologists and channel persons from Europe who like to help people with their lifes. Therefore we create skills which can give you hints about upcoming "things" that might impact your life - or we just give you hints that might set a point in your life. In Today's Prophecy you get a quote that reflects the current constellation of stars for you. So listen to it carefully and think what to do...
